settings.description: Luigi has teamed up with bowser to take over the mushroom kingdom using the advanced P-wing, Mario must take the advanced P-wing from the chest to halfway stop the invasion.
Cannons to the LEFT of me.. BOOTS! BOOTS! Bullets to the RIGHT o' me.. BOMBS! BOMBS! I'm going mad.. it's the desert madness! AAAAA! -- at the end of room 2, the warp exit is under the centre block.
What? How can this day get any worse?!
Luigi must take the hammer bro suit on his airship and take it to bowser.
You and your crew are on vacation when a anomaly strikes your ship and you and your crew evacuates! You find your ship safe but 4 of your crewmates are missing! Find them! Based off: VVVVVV
The universal gravitation of this ball is ALL topsy turvy! No wonder they never used this thing officially!
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the airship section, and the transition to desert land.
